{
  "texts": [
    "Both the outputs of the Huber and null generators were weighted by the same anatomical prior as the FCNET.",
    "For each model and fold, we tested the left-out network with 6 different metrics (see Methods).",
    "The results for each score are shown in Table 1 for the mean and in Table S1 for each subject in the dataset.",
    "FCNET significantly outperforms the null model in all evaluation metrics (p < 0.001 two-tailed U-test).",
    "When tested against the Huber regressor, FCNET outperformed it in the metrics assessing numerical reconstructions (p < 0.05 two-tailed U-test; for MSE and MAE) as well as metrics assessing similarity (p ~0.05 two-tailed U-test; for PCC and CS)."
  ]
}